	(add_scroll_timeout), (gtk_tree_view_drag_motion): factor out
	add_scroll_timeout().  (Backfolded to upstream).

2007-01-18  Michael Natterer  <mitch@imendio.com>

	* gtk/gtkcheckbutton.c
	* gtk/gtkdnd.c
	* gtk/gtkentry.c
	* gtk/gtkmenu.c
	* gtk/gtktreeview.c
